{"tid":1675954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FC方法之一，記得起下底先","createTime":"2019-10-26T07:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T10:44:11.000Z","uid":222524,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"900c25f9db2d712795b2dab2205b7bf375269a67","tid":1675954,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:16:27.000Z","msg":"給沒有獨立思考的你：<br />\n<br />\nFC方法有好多<br />\n呢個係一個比較簡單既FC方法<br />\n<br />\n以後想知一件事係咪俾人帶風向<br />\n睇下出post者個底，睇下佢以往係咪三毛定啊sir<br />\n不過有時出post者未必係鬼<br />\n咁所以要睇埋下面留言個d<br />\n要睇多幾個個底<br />\n留意下個d會員平時留言係講開d咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8bfcac05fa2074c29457e6330cdab9712eab50","tid":1675954,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:18:21.000Z","msg":"希望大家俾like我呢個post，好多五毛滲透咗：<br />\n<br />\n【瓦解分化妙計】建議連仔<span style=\"color: red;\">加設五毛、分化撚、mon post狗</span>等標籤識別功能，並以<span style=\"color: red;\">唔同顏色</span>顯示該等被標籤嘅用戶名俾自己睇（標籤唔會公開，但連仔有紀錄追蹤）<br />\n <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669672\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669672</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"21afd42f6f3f67bc9a2e8b55f64093370b25508c","tid":1675954,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2bea0c037299d9d3bd29dbbd5086bfd5643c56","tid":1675954,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40bdb9e3f56fe3bcfedece2465e7d6720f47f6c","tid":1675954,"uid":135328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:24:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n4個月了要識諗了"},{"pid":"d42c59e099e17c74f86cf0ea589fedc89942deea","tid":1675954,"uid":277263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GHdQTdv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://